l": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eCast", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Laverne_%26_Shirley_(1981_TV_series)"}
{"title_page": "P\u00ebrlepnic\u00eb Lake", "text_new": "{{Unreferenced|date=December 2008}}\n{{Infobox lake\n| name = P\u00ebrlepnic\u00eb Lake <br /> \u0408\u0435\u0437\u0435\u0440\u043e \u041f\u0440\u0438\u043b\u0435\u043f\u043d\u0438\u0446\u0430 / Jezero Prilepnica\n| image =\n| caption =\n| image_bathymetry =\n| caption_bathymetry =\n| location = [[Goljak]] Mountains, eastern [[Kosovo]]\n| coords = {{coord|42|31|35|N|21|30|46|E|type:waterbody|display=inline,title}}\n| lake_type =\n| inflow =\n| outflow =\n| catchment =\n| basin_countries = Kosovo\n| length = {{convert|1.4|km|abbr=on}}\n| width = {{convert|300|m|abbr=on}}\n| area = {{convert|0.18|km2|abbr=on}}\n| depth =\n| max-depth =\n| volume =\n| residence_time =\n| shore =\n| elevation = {{convert|620|m|ft|abbr=on}}\n| islands =\n| sections =\n| cities =\n| frozen =\n}}\n'''P\u00ebrlepnic\u00eb Lake''' ({{lang-sq|Liqeni i P\u00ebrlepnic\u00ebs}}, {{lang-sr|\u0408\u0435\u0437\u0435\u0440\u043e \u041f\u0440\u0438\u043b\u0435\u043f\u043d\u0438\u0446\u0430}} / Jezero Prilepnica) is a small [[lake]] situated in western [[Kosovo]], surrounded by the [[Goljak]] mountains. Prilepnica Lake is found just north-east of the city of [[Gjilan]], also it supplies water for the city. A tributary of the [[South Morava]] flows through the lake and it is the largest lake in the east of Kosovo.\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Perlepnice Lake}}\n[[Category:Lakes of Kosovo]]\n\n\n{{Kosovo-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Unreferenced|date=December 2008}}\n{{Infobox lake\n| name = P\u00ebrlepnic\u00eb Lake <br /> \u0408\u0435\u0437\u0435\u0440\u043e \u041f\u0440\u0438\u043b\u0435\u043f\u043d\u0438\u0446\u0430\n| image =\n| caption =\n| image_bathymetry =\n| caption_bathymetry =\n| location = [[Goljak]] mountains, Eastern Kosovo\n| coords = {{coord|42|31|35|N|21|30|46|E|type:waterbody|display=inline,title}}\n| lake_type =\n| inflow =\n| outflow =\n| catchment =\n| basin_countries = Kosovo\n| length = {{convert|1.4|km|abbr=on}}\n| width = {{convert|300|m|abbr=on}}\n| area = {{convert|0.18|km2|abbr=on}}\n| depth =\n| max-depth =\n| volume =\n| residence_time =\n| shore =\n| elevation = {{convert|620|m|ft|abbr=on}}\n| islands =\n| sections =\n| cities =\n| frozen =\n}}\n'''P\u00ebrlepnic\u00eb Lake''' ({{lang-sq|Liqeni i P\u00ebrlepnic\u00ebs}}, {{lang-sr|\u0408\u0435\u0437\u0435\u0440\u043e \u041f\u0440\u0438\u043b\u0435\u043f\u043d\u0438\u0446\u0430}}) is a small [[lake]] situated in western [[Kosovo]], surrounded by the [[Goljak]] mountains. Prilepnica Lake is found just north-east of the city of [[Gjilan]], also it supplies water for the city. A tributary of the [[South Morava]] flows through the lake and it is the largest lake in the east of Kosovo.\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Perlepnice Lake}}\n[[Category:Lakes of Kosovo]]\n\n\n{{Kosovo-geo-stub}}\n", "name_user": "SrpskiAnonimac", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/P%C3%ABrlepnic%C3%AB_Lake"}
